text: Philippe Tisson (1905 - 25 September 1985) was a French swimmer. He competed in the men's 4 × 200 metre freestyle relay event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1985 deaths Category:French male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:French male freestyle swimmers
